bhaji in problem ( punjabi : ਭਾਜੀ ਇਨ ਪ੍ਰਾਬਲਮ ) is a 2013 indian punjabi-language comedy film directed by smeep kang , who had earlier directed films like carry on jatta and lucky di unlucky story , both of which featured gippy grewal in the lead role .   grewal also appears in this film , along with an ensemble cast including ragini khanna , gurpreet ghuggi , b.n. sharma , karamjit anmol , japji khaira , khushboo grewal and misha bajwa amongst others .   the film is produced by ashvini yardi , and bollywood actor akshay kumar who also appears in the film shortly , enacting as a lookalike of himself .   aside from akshay kumar , the film also features actor om puri and cricketer harbhajan singh .   bhaji in problem was released on 15 november 2013 .   it has released in over 600 screens worldwide .